com.interpss.se.record

Interface SEBranchRecord

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SEBranchRecordImpl

    public interface SEBranchRecord
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable
    A representation of the model object 'SE Branch Record'. SE branch data record class.

    The following features are supported:

    • PSe Rec
    • QSe Rec
    • Cur Se Rec
    • Tap Se Rec
    • PJ Matrix Index
    • QJ Matrix Index
    See Also:
    SERecordPackage.getSEBranchRecord()
